Recommended Compilation Directions

To compile for Linux:
	1) Install the dependency packages: libtar-dev, libssl-dev, zlib1g-dev
	2) Compile using "make" in the tool's directory
	
To compile for OSX:
	1) Get MacPorts
	2) Install the packages: libtar, openssl, zlib
	3) Open the Xcode 4 project and compile
	
To compile for Windows:
	1) Get Cygwin
	2) Install the packages: openssl-devel, zlib-devel
	3) Compile and install libtar
	4) Compile using "make" in the tool's directory
